Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:04.90,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H05F4F5&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord4}如果有人說那是奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:10.36,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0500FB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}和你緊緊相連的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:15.49,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H64CB00&\3c&HFFFFFF&}除了「心靈感應」還能是什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:18.16,ed,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFB4EF8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}啦啦啦 再再再 再發現！
